pve-storage-ontap-nvmetcp (1.1-2) stable; urgency=medium

  * fix: get_formats() returns the 'valid'/'default' keys expected by
    PVE::Storage::Plugin (were 'formats'/'default_format', silently ignored).
    Thanks PandemiK911 (#2).
  * fix: volume_snapshot_info() reports a stable id for consistency-group
    snapshots; list_cg_snapshots() now fetches the uuid field. Thanks
    PandemiK911 (#3).
  * feat: on_update_hook_full() removes the secret file when a sensitive
    property is deleted (pvesm set --delete), instead of leaving it orphaned.
    Thanks PandemiK911 (#4).

